                <expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">T</supplied>i</abbr><ex>berio</ex></expan> Claudio <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Secundino <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>IIvir</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">A</supplied>rtoriae <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> Flora<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Lucullo <lb n="6"/>|(centurioni) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIIII |(centurioni) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIII <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">Se</supplied>cundo <lb n="8"/>Valeria Crispa <lb n="9"/>fecit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundjahr: zwischen 1826 und 1831 in der zweiten Abbruchphase des Alten Turms. In Z. 1, 2, 4 und 5 sind über den langen Vokalen Apices gesetzt. M. Claudius Lucullus war centurio der legio XIIII und der XIII gemina. Z. 6: zweimal die Sigle für centurio. Z. 7: Ligatur ND. In Z. 1, 2, 4 und 5 sind über den langen Vokalen Apices gesetzt.</p>
            </div>
